data.description: Step into elegance at the Kings River Village, 6810 Amber Ash Court. This beautifully renovated and dreamy floor plan offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full, 1-1/2 baths, located in a CUL-DE-SAC! Enjoy a grand entryway with engineered hardwood floors leading from the living room to the kitchen. The kitchen includes an open floor plan, with a breakfast room and an attached formal dining room. Amazing natural lighting all throughout the home, huge windows with a fireplace.The primary suite located on the first floor has double doors leading to separate sinks, separate bath, and shower, and TWO large closets. Upstairs is a game room overlooking the living room, with 2 multifunctional bedrooms, a full-size bathroom with a tub. The backyard and garage are both large with tons of room for tools, for landscaping, and a garden! Kings River Village has so much to offer, such as walking trails, a community pool, and recreational parks. The potential Is endless with this beautiful MOVE IN READY home.
